---
import "./CardTeach.css";
---

<article class="round no-elevate p-0 wave">
  <div class="gfx gfx-teach" role="img" aria-label="Concentric ripples expanding outward from a glowing core, suggesting knowledge spreading">
    <span class="core"></span>
    <span class="ripple ra"></span>
    <span class="ripple rb"></span>
    <span class="ripple rc"></span>
  </div>
  <div class="p-5">
    <h3 class="text-3 lh-2 fw-6">Teach</h3>
    <p class="mt-2 text-1 italic">For senior practitioners who want depth.</p>
    <p class="text-0 mt-2">Everything we learn by building and advising becomes the foundation of what we teach. Stackdemy, our technical education platform, shares the state-of-the-art techniques that come directly from our practice.</p>
    <a class="link mt-2 text-0" href="https://stackdemy.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Explore Stackdemy →</a>
  </div>
</article>
